==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Marian
<hw>Ma"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to the
<person>Virgin Mary</person>, or sometimes to <person>Mary, Queen of
England</person>, daughter of <person>Henry VIII</person>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Of all the <qex>Marian</qex> martyrs, Mr. Philpot was the
best-born gentleman.</q> <rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Maid Marian</b></col>. <sd>(a)</sd> <cd>See
<er>Maidmarian</er> in the Vocabulary.</cd> <sd>(a)</sd> <cd>A prominent
character in the legend of Robin Hood.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Marie</ent>⟦br⟧
